u8232 the steep walls of the city, the father of gods and men\u8232 came down from heaven, sat on the peaks of Ida,\u8232 with its many springs, holding a thunderbolt.\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0210\u8232 He sent off gold-winged Iris with a message:\
